Cronos II (Scratch) 0.3.0-pre1

Cronos II is the open source mail client for the Gnome Desktop.

It features many advanced characteristics that will help
you in your day to day work with  communications and
mailing necessities.

Though Cronos II is being actively developed and is being
worked on  by the Cronos II Hackers Team permanently this is
version is still BETA software.
Currently its able to handle everything without any problem,
but this does not mean you might find some problem with it.

If you do, please, mail the Cronos II Hackers Team with
the problems you encountered and every piece of information
you can give so the Team can work to fix your problems.

Thanks for choosing us.


